name: You Ain’t the First
lyrics:
I tried so hard just to get through to you
But your head’s so far From the realness of truth
Was it just a come on in the dark
I think you’ve worn your welcome honey
I’ll just see you along as I sing you this song
Time can pass slowly Things always change
Your day’s been numbered And I’ve read your last page
You was just a temporary love
But honey you ain’t the first
Lots of other come before you woman
Said you been the worst
So goodbye to you girl
I can’t hear you cryin’ Your jivin’s been hell
So look for me walkin’ Down your street at night
I’ll be in with another Deep down inside
